sentences: The band was started in 1988 by the brothers D Thrilla and K9 the sonic Maximizer of the Queens Village neighborhood of New York City.
The group was formed primarily to play a battle of the bands at the local Queens Village church Our Lady of Lourdes in 1988.
No Redeeming Social Value had a run on the local Queens Heavy Metal circuit in the late 1980s and early 1990s.
